							| communities that never stop learning.
						br
						p
							| If you want to go fast, go alone. 
							| If you want to go far, go together. 
							| “African proverb”.
					a.button(href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1J28n6d2RpPAoIoOryzlSeT8IOs8QHsaJ?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer")  
